fun existsByBlockerIdAndBlockedId(blockerId: String, blockedId: String): Boolean
```

### After (IN 쿼리로 일괄 조회):

```kotlin
interface BlockRepository : JpaRepository<BlockEntity, String> {
    // 차단 목록 일괄 조회 (IN 쿼리)
    @Query("""
        SELECT b.blockedId 
        FROM BlockEntity b 
        WHERE b.blockerId = :blockerId 
          AND b.blockedId IN :targetUserIds
    """)
    fun findBlockedUserIds(
        @Param("blockerId") blockerId: String,
        @Param("targetUserIds") targetUserIds: List<String>,
    ): List<String>
}
```

예상 개선: N회 쿼리 -> 1회 IN 쿼리, 100ms -> 5ms

